<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Feb1937"><font color="red">1 February 1937</font> <i>NLGC</i> (from Gerald Griffin to Paul L&eacute;on): Could you let me know &hellip; if <cite>Ulysses</cite> is on the Index Expurgationes of the Holy See? &hellip; I presume you have got the copy of the O.R. &hellip; I posted it yesterday. </div>
